high_descs: Cross the room to stand in front of the end piece of counter space to the right of the stove.
Pick up the salt shaker from the counter.
Back up a couple steps from the counter while holding the salt.
Open the top drawer beneath the counter and place the salt in the back left corner of the drawer.
Turn and move to the counter to the left of the kitchen sink.
Pick up the salt shaker from the counter.
Turn and move back to the counter to the right of the stove.
Open that top drawer again, and place the salt shaker to the right of the other shaker you previously put inside.
anns.task_desc: Move two salt shakers to a drawer by the stove.

high_descs: Walk forward, turn to the left to face the counter top.
Pick up the salt shaker that is in front of the loaf of bread.
Turn around then back around to face the counter top.
Open the drawer, place the salt on the left back side of the drawer.
Turn around and face the other cabinet.
Pick up the salt on the counter top behind the drinking glass.
Turn around to face the cabinet with the toaster.
Open the drawer and place the salt shaker next to the other salt shaker and close the door.
anns.task_desc: Pick up and move the salt to the drawer under the toaster.

high_descs: Walk forward and then turn to your left
Pick up the shaker of salt off of the kitchen counter
Take a step back from where you were standing
Open the drawer, put the salt in and close the drawer
Turn around and walk to the counter again
Pick up another shaker of salt off of the kitchen counter
Turn around and face the way you were before
Open the drawer, put the other salt in and close the drawer
anns.task_desc: Put two salt shakers in the kitchen drawer
